🚀 Excited to Share My Cybersecurity Project – Sentinel Threat Trace! 🔐

As part of my cybersecurity learning journey, I built Sentinel Threat Trace, a web-based platform designed to spread awareness about phishing attacks while demonstrating how phishing detection and user education can work together.

This project helped me strengthen my understanding of:
✅ Phishing attack techniques and prevention
✅ Cybersecurity awareness and secure browsing practices
✅ Web application development
✅ User-focused security solutions
✅ Problem-solving and project deployment

Building this project gave me valuable hands-on experience in combining cybersecurity concepts with practical implementation. It reinforced the importance of educating users, as human error continues to be one of the biggest security risks.

🌐 Live Demo: https://sentinel-theta-brown.vercel.app/

